  "texts": [
    "Agentic AI marks a fundamental shift beyond conventional generative systems, transitioning from reactive, prompt-based interactions to autonomous agents capable of sustained decision-making.",
    "This transformation promises remarkable efficiency and innovation-but it also introduces new complexities and risks that span legal, economic, and creative domains.",
    "First, agentic AI radically reshapes creativity and intellectual property.",
    "By independently generating novel ideas and structures, these systems challenge traditional assumptions about authorship and ownership.",
    "When an autonomous agent can produce highly original-and potentially valuable-outputs, the conventional rationale for incentivizing human creativity becomes less clear."
  ],
